# Financial Risk Management Capital Expense Reserve Offset Statutory Capital Amount

## identifier
de5358

## type
float

## definition
Report the amount of Statutory Capital which has been utilised in meeting the expense reserve requirement of all statutory funds in accordance with the solvency prudential standard and in meeting

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.ManagementCapital.ExpenseReserveOffsetStatutoryCapital.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
